sub_title:
Teacher of Dutch as a foreign language NT2
Experienced Office Manager & Fitness trainer, specialized in kids and youth.
summary:
Driven and empathic teacher of Dutch as a second language. For expats and civil integration (inburgering). Levels A0-C1. Groups and individuals. Experience with in person and on-line lessons.
For more info: thdonbv.nl
